{"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}}}